message: /sp.constitution Create a Constitution document for a book about "Physical AI and Humanoid Robotics" with these requirements: -Target audience: beginners to intermediate -Tech stack : Docusaurus for Documentation - Focus on hands-0n learning .Provide the constitution with: Vision, Core Principles, Success Criteria, Constraints, Stakeholders, and Brand Voice.

/sp.tasks Break down the plan into specific executable tasks as a chechlist. Include: 1. Docusaurus setup tasks 2. Chapter  development tasks (for 1 chapter with 3 lessons)
/sp.implement implement the 001-book-structure-spec/ you have already this folder and update this
